US Bank  Alert Message 



  We
recently reviewed your account, and we suspect an unauthorized ATM -
based transactions on your account. Therefore, as a preventive measure
we have temporary limited your access to sensitive US Bank features.
 


To
ensure that your account is not compromised please login to US Bank 
Internet Banking by clicking this link, verify your identity and your
online account will be reactivated by our system. 



- Click on: 
http://online.usbank.com/logon/logon.asp?dd=1


- Enter your personal information.


  - Verify your identity with US Bank 


  If
at any time you require assistance, please contact our Online Account
Services customer hotline at 1-800-788-7000 24 hours a day, 7 days a
week.


Thank you for using US Bank  Online Account Services.


		

		

		




Important Information from US Bank (R)

  
This e-mail contains information directly related to your account with  us, other

  services
to which you have subscribed, and/or any application you may have
submitted. US Bank and its service providers are committed to
protecting your privacy and ask you not to send sensitive account
information through e-mail. You can view our privacy policy and contact
information at http://usbank.com  . If you are not a US Bank customer and believe you received this
message in error, please notify us by responding to this e-mail.
